column2: SELECT top # sp.ra, sp.dec, sp.z, sp.class, sp.subclass, sp.psfmag_u-sp.extinction_u AS mag_u, sp.psfmag_g-sp.extinction_g AS mag_g, sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r AS mag_r, sp.psfmag_i-sp.extinction_i AS mag_i, sp.psfmag_z-sp.extinction_z AS mag_z, w.w1mpro AS w1, w.w2mpro AS w2, w.w3mpro AS w3, w.w4mpro AS w4, so.velDisp, so.elodieFeH, so.elodieSpType, so.elodieBV, so.elodieTEff, so.elodieLogG FROM SpecPhoto AS sp JOIN wise_xmatch AS xm ON sp.objid = xm.sdss_objid JOIN wise_allsky AS w ON xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr JOIN SpecObj AS so ON sp.objid = so.bestObjID WHERE (sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r > #)
